<div class="container" style="padding: 0;">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <div id="result" >
        <a href="<%= $SUB_DIRECTORY %>/img/sample.png" data-lightbox="sample">
          <img style="max-width:100%; max-height:100%; " alt="RSyntaxTree Sample" src="<%= $SUB_DIRECTORY %>/img/sample.png" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="text-right" style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; line-height: 100%;">
        <small>
          左クリックでズーム，右クリックで画像保存<br />
          画像エリアとテキストエリアは縦方向にサイズ変更可能
        </small>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <div id="status" style="min-height:1.5em; padding-left: 1em; margin-top: 5px; background-color: #484848	;">
        <span id="alert">
          <span class="text text-info">●</span> <span class="alertmessage"></span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="anchor" id="rst-editor"></div>

      <div id="editor"><%= $SAMPLE1 %></div>

      <div class="text-right" style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px; line-height: 100%;">
        <small>
          バージョン1.0では，樹形図描画の構文が大幅に刷新されました．詳しくは<br /> <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/rsyntaxtree/documentation_ja">使い方</a> および <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://yohasebe.github.io/rsyntaxtree/examples">ギャラリー</a> を参照してください．
        </small>
      </div>

      <div  class="text-right">
        <div class="row" style="margin-top:15px; margin-bottom:15px;">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div style="display:inline">
              <input type="checkbox" value="" id="auto-bracket">
              <label for="auto-bracket">
                <small>括弧を自動で閉じる</small>
              </label>&nbsp;&nbsp;
            </div>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-light" id="check"><i class="far fa-check-square"></i><small> 括弧の対応チェック</small></button>&nbsp;
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-light" id="clear"><i class="fas fa-eraser"></i><small> クリア</small></button>&nbsp;
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-light" id="insert-backslash" title="バックスラッシュを挿入">\</button>&nbsp;
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-light" id="insert-bar" title="縦線を挿入">|</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:15px;">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-info" id="toggle-ipa-keyboard" title="クリックしてIPA音声記号パネルの表示/非表示を切り替え"><i class="fas fa-keyboard"></i> IPAキーボード</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="ipa-keyboard-panel" style="display:none; margin-bottom:15px;">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
              <ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="ipa-tabs" role="tablist">
                <li class="nav-item">
                  <a class="nav-link active" id="vowels-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#vowels" role="tab">母音</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                  <a class="nav-link" id="consonants-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#consonants" role="tab">子音</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                  <a class="nav-link" id="diacritics-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#diacritics" role="tab">補助記号</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                  <a class="nav-link" id="suprasegmentals-tab" data-toggle="tab" href="#suprasegmentals" role="tab">超分節音</a>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <div class="tab-content" id="ipa-tab-content" style="padding-top: 10px;">
                <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="vowels" role="tabpanel"></div>
                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="consonants" role="tabpanel"></div>
                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="diacritics" role="tabpanel"></div>
                <div class="tab-pane fade" id="suprasegmentals" role="tabpanel"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:15px; margin-top:15px;">
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <button class="btn btn-primary draw btn-block" id="draw_png" type="button"><i class="fas fa-image"></i> Draw <b>PNG</b></button>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <button class="btn btn-primary draw btn-block" id="draw_svg" type="button"><i class="fas fa-vector-square"></i> Draw <b>SVG</b></button>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <button class="btn btn-secondary draw btn-block" id="download_pdf" type="button"><i class="fas fa-file-pdf"></i> Download <b>PDF</b></button>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container" style="margin-top: 40px; padding: 0;">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <label for="leafstyle">コネクタの形状</label>
      <select class="form-control" name="leafstyle" id="leafstyle">
        <option value="auto">自動</option>
        <option value="bar">縦線のみ</option>
        <option value="nothing">なし</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <label for="fontstyle">フォント・スタイル</label>
      <select class="form-control" name="fontstyle" id="fontstyle">
        <option value="noto-serif">Noto Serif</option>
        <option value="noto-sans">Noto Sans</option>
        <option value="noto-sans-mono">Noto Sans Mono</option>
        <option value="cjk">WQY Zen Hei (CJK)</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <label for="fontsize">フォント・サイズ</label>
      <select class="form-control" name="fontsize" id="fontsize">
        <option value="6">6</option>
        <option value="8">8</option>
        <option value="10">10</option>
        <option value="12">12</option>
        <option value="14">14</option>
        <option selected="selected" value="16">16</option>
        <option value="18">18</option>
        <option value="20">20</option>
        <option value="22">22</option>
        <option value="24">24</option>
        <option value="26">26</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <label for="color">カラー</label>
      <select class="form-control" name="color" id="color">
        <option value="modern">Modern</option>
        <option value="traditional" selected="selected">Traditional</option>
        <option value="none">なし</option>
      </select>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <label for="vheight">コネクタの高さ</label>
      <select class="form-control" name="vheight" id="vheight">
        <option value="0.5">0.5</option>
        <option value="1.0">1.0</option>
        <option value="1.5">1.5</option>
        <option value="2.0" selected="selected">2.0</option>
        <option value="3.0">3.0</option>
        <option value="4.0">4.0</option>
        <option value="5.0">5.0</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <label for="linewidth">線の幅</label>
      <select class="form-control" name="linewidth" id="linewidth">
        <option value="1" selected="selected">1</option>
        <option value="2">2</option>
        <option value="3">3</option>
        <option value="4">4</option>
        <option value="5">5</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3"></div>
    <div class="col-md-3"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="polyline">折れ線コネクタ</label><br />
        <div class="btn-group btn-group-toggle" data-toggle="buttons">
          <label class="btn btn-light active">
            <input type="radio" name="polyline" id="polyline-on" value="on" autocomplete="off"> On
          </label>
          <label class="btn btn-light">
            <input type="radio" name="polyline" id="polyline-off" value="off" autocomplete="off" checked> Off
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="transparent">背景の透過</label><br />
        <div class="btn-group btn-group-toggle" data-toggle="buttons">
          <label class="btn btn-light">
            <input type="radio" name="transparent" id="transparent-on" value="on" autocomplete="off"> On
          </label>
          <label class="btn btn-light active">
            <input type="radio" name="transparent" id="transparent-off" value="off" autocomplete="off" checked> Off
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="symmetrize">極端な左右対象化</label><br />
        <div class="btn-group btn-group-toggle" data-toggle="buttons">
          <label class="btn btn-light">
            <input type="radio" name="symmetrize" id="symmetrize-on" value="on" autocomplete="off"> On
          </label>
          <label class="btn btn-light active">
            <input type="radio" name="symmetrize" id="symmetrize-off" value="off" autocomplete="off" checked> Off
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-3">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="hide_default_connectors">コネクタを隠す</label><br />
        <div class="btn-group btn-group-toggle" data-toggle="buttons">
          <label class="btn btn-light active">
            <input type="radio" name="hide_default_connectors" id="hide_default_connectors-on" value="on" autocomplete="off"> On
          </label>
          <label class="btn btn-light">
            <input type="radio" name="hide_default_connectors" id="hide_default_connectors-off" value="off" autocomplete="off" checked> Off
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
